{"productOptionsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p class=\"text-neutral-600\">Use this section for <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">ordering rules</strong>: style number, price band, minimums, and stated production time from the supplier catalog. Final invoice may reflect decoration, proofs, rush, or freight.</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Field</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Value</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Style #</td><td class=\"py-2 font-mono text-neutral-900\">30181</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">List price range</td><td class=\"py-2\">$159.11 – $262.59 USD</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Minimum quantity</td><td class=\"py-2\">5</td></tr>\n<tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-500 align-top\">Stated production time</td><td class=\"py-2\">5 days</td></tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Quantity pricing (USD)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-2\">Price per unit at each order-quantity break (from the live product page).</p>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse text-left text-[13px]\">\n<thead><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-200 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-500\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-3 font-medium\">Quantity</th><th class=\"py-2 font-medium\">Price (each)</th></tr></thead>\n<tbody><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">5</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$262.59 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">10</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$231.07 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">25</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$203.67 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">50</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$179.83 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">125</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$159.11 each</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Catalog highlights</h4><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[13px] leading-snug\"><li>Made Of Recycled 1680D Ballistic Nylon With Recycled 210D Polyester Velvet Lining.</li><li>Adjustable/Detachable Padded Shoulder Strap And Web Carrying Handles With Snap Closure Comfort Grip.</li><li>Genuine Leather Handle Wrap, Shoulder Strap Pad, Trim and Touchpoints.</li><li>Double Zippered Main Compartment .</li><li>Double Zippered Front Pocket.</li></ul>\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mb-2\">Patch options (supplier)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-3\">Options and add-ons from the live Distributor Central product page for this SKU. Pricing may change; confirm on your quote.</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50/30\">\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Product Style</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-op